Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:21.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,着いた！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:21.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:23.42,Default JP,,0,0,0,,市営グラウンドだぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:23.42,Default CN,,0,0,0,,是市運動場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:27.42,Default JP,,0,0,0,,すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:27.42,Default CN,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.97,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ベローネ学院  高等部のサッカー部は...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.97,Default CN,,0,0,0,,請問菲諾奈學院高中部的足球部是在...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:39.10,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ひかり
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:39.10,Default CN,,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:41.13,Default JP,,0,0,0,,溢れてるポポ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:41.13,Default CN,,0,0,0,,滿出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:45.85,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ひかり  どうしたポポ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:45.85,Default CN,,0,0,0,,光 你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:47.72,Default JP,,0,0,0,,どうしたルル？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:47.72,Default CN,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:50.32,Default JP,,0,0,0,,変ポポ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:50.32,Default CN,,0,0,0,,不對勁...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:53.07,Default JP,,0,0,0,,さっきから  ずっと変ポポ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:53.07,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你從剛才開始就一直很不對勁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:55.45,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ううん  なんでもない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:55.45,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:58.97,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ひかりに何かあったら  嫌ポポ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:58.97,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我不想你出事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:00.45,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ルルンも嫌ルル...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:00.45,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我也不想...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.65,0:11:06.95,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ポルン  ルルン  ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.65,0:11:06.95,Default CN,,0,0,0,,保倫 露露 謝謝你們這麼關心我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:08.32,Default JP,,0,0,0,,大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:08.32,Default CN,,0,0,0,,但我不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:09.70,Default JP,,0,0,0,,きっと大丈夫よ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:09.70,Default CN,,0,0,0,,肯定會沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:10.60,Default JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ひかりさん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:10.60,Default CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:12.95,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ほのかポポ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:12.95,Default CN,,0,0,0,,穗乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:15.30,Default JP,,0,0,0,,どうしたんですか？こんな所に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:15.30,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你怎麼到這來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:19.07,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎさが  市営グラウンドに来てるって  聞いたから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:19.07,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我聽說 渚到市運動場來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:21.07,Default JP,,0,0,0,,やっぱり  気になっちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:21.07,Default CN,,0,0,0,,因為我還是不太放心她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:22.57,Default JP,,0,0,0,,私も  つい...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:22.57,Default CN,,0,0,0,,所以 就...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:26.87,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎささんも  この近くに  ですか...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:26.87,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚也在這附近啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:28.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:28.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:30.20,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あの...ひかりさん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:30.20,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我說...光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:31.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:31.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:34.67,Default JP,,0,0,0,,大丈夫？最近  何か  ちょっと..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:34.67,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧？你最近好像有點...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:35.65,Default JP,,0,0,0,,変ミポ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:35.65,Default CN,,0,0,0,,不對勁！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:36.67,Default JP,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:36.67,Default CN,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:39.58,Default JP,,0,0,0,,邪悪な気配を感じるミポ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:39.58,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我感受到邪惡的氣息了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:42.02,Default JP,,0,0,0,,早く  なぎさたちの所に行くミポ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:42.02,Default CN,,0,0,0,,快到渚那裡去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:49.47,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ひかり
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:49.47,Default CN,,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:52.10,Default JP,,0,0,0,,そろそろ  ひと休みしようか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:52.10,Default CN,,0,0,0,,差不多該休息啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:53.20,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:53.20,Default CN,,0,0,0,,啊？
